Date: 1998-10-22

Title: Entropy of 2+1 dimensional de Sitter space in terms of brick wall method

Authors: Won Tae Kim

Comments: 6pages, revtex, no figures to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D59 (1999) 047503

We calculate the statistical entropy of a scalar field on the background ofthree-dimensional De Sitter space in terms of the brick wall method and finallyderive the perimeter law of the entropy.